msgctxt "68_Tanimura"
msgid "(Damn... These bastards were one step ahead of me!)"
msgstr "(Carajo... ¡Estos bastardos estaban un paso delante de mi!)"

msgctxt "80_Tanimura"
msgid "I'll be taking that bag off your hands."
msgstr "Voy a quitarles esa bolsa de las manos."

msgctxt "92_Tough Guy"
msgid "Ah, so you know what this is? Glad you showed up, then. Now we can get rid of you."
msgstr "¡Ah, así que sabes lo que es? que bueno que apareciste entonces. Ahora podemos deshacerte de ti."

